How to use this script:
* Download it
git clone https://github.com/FloraMaeWolfe/dragonfire-minetest-client-linux-compile.git

* Change permissions as needed:
chmod +x dragonfire-compile-linux.sh

* Run it:
./dragonfire-compile-linux.sh


NOTES:
* This script is currently experimental. It has only been verified to work on Linux Mint 21.2. Other distros have not been tested yet.
* Supported distros include: Ubuntu, Ubuntu-based, Linux Mint, Debian, Fedora, Arch, Arch-based, Alpine, and Alpine-based.
* This script may break with distro upgrades. If it breaks or if something is missing, please create an issue ticket so it can be fixed.
* If you enjoy my work and want to support me and my work, there is a file with information on how to do so. 
